code: public static Direction from(OrderDirection dir) {     return dir == null || dir == OrderDirection.ASC ? ASC : DESC. }
public SortOrder asOrder() {     return this == Direction.ASC ? SortOrder.ASC : SortOrder.DESC. }
public static Missing from(NullsPosition pos) {     return pos == null || pos == NullsPosition.FIRST ? FIRST : LAST. }
